恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 23 Aug 2023 11:35:19 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692789507</ingested><modified> 2023-08-23T11:18:31+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="825" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/ac0ec3e0-4197-11ee-9df7-aa3c67cc596d" width="1100"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="825" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/ac0ec3e0-4197-11ee-9df7-aa3c67cc596d" width="1100"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[TOM PENPARK]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A woman works at a standing desk with two monitors facing her.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[CORSAIR Platform:6]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The Morning After: Atari’s new miniature console plays 2600 and 7800 game carts]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>经过 <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-03-31-atari-vcs-final-design.html">最后的努力</a>，雅达利正在推出另一款复古家用游戏机。 <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ataris-2600-is-a-miniature-console-that-plays-2600-and-7800-game-carts-171014464.html">Atari 2600+</a>向 1977 年推出的原版 Atari 2600 致敬，但这款重制版呼应了 1980 年的四开关型号。（当然，我们会具体说明。）</p> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/ataris-2600-is-a-minia