现已第二次推迟。 2016 年<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-07-25-rpg-hyper-light-drifter-pixel-2d-ios.html"><em>《Hyper Light Drifter》</em></a>的精神继承者的发布窗口现已重新安排在 2024 年初。</p><p>开发商 Heart Machine 的创始人兼创意总监 Alx Preston 在宣布推迟的<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://youtu.be/InuOjewX_-s">视频</a>中表示：“因此，在推出抢先体验之前，我们还需要在<em>《Hyper Light Breaker》</em>上多花一点时间。” “这意味着我们将把日期推迟到明年初，即 2024 年。”他表示，额外的时间将“让我们能够充分发挥游戏的潜力。”普雷斯顿感谢粉丝们的耐心和支持，并承诺“一场新的冒险将不辜负粉丝们对《心脏机器》游戏的期望。” </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3584d8a0-4128-11ee-b9bc-05e8141f84a5" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3584d8a0-4128-11ee-b9bc-05e8141f84a5" style="height:2160px;width:3840px;" alt="即将推出的游戏“Hyper Light Breaker”的宣传照。一个角色沿着建筑物的废墟冲浪，准备从末端跳下去。背景中可以看到沙漠地形和废墟。" data-uuid="7b1d6b01-1767-3575-b895-abee03c0e144"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">心脏机器/齿轮箱出版</div></figure><p><em>Hyper Light Breaker</em>将游戏玩法从 2D 转变为 3D，同时最多可添加三名玩家进行合作游戏。虽然 2016 年的原创游戏沿用了经典自上而下的塞尔达传说游戏的元素，但即将推出的开放世界游戏也融入了一些<em>《荒野之息》的</em>基础知识。其中包括探索散布着废墟的开阔乡村，同时乘坐滑翔机在空中翱翔和从山上冲浪。然而， <em>《Hyper Light Breaker》</em>使用程序生成的环境，这应该有助于提高可重玩性。它的战斗似乎也与任天堂的现代塞尔达游戏<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.gameinformer.com/exclusive-video/2023/04/11/meet-hyper-light-breakers-last-master-miniboss-with-director-alx-preston">不同</a>。 <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/first-hyper-light-breaker-gameplay-trailer-reveals-fall-early-access-release-161516775.html">游戏的第一个预告片</a>让您可以近距离了解。</p><p> “我们有很多疯狂的想法想要融入到游戏中，这是令人兴奋和激动的，因为我们创建的格式和技术允许如此多的可能性，”普雷斯顿说。 “这一短暂的推动将为我们提供最好的机会，以便在明年的抢先体验开放开发中迈出更强有力的第一步。” </p><div id="1833d50599c44430a7b77dc96d2b6f5f"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/InuOjewX_-s" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/hyper-light-breaker-early-access-pushed-back-to-early-2024-205056875.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/hyper-light-breaker-early-access-pushed-back-to-early-2024-205056875.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 407aad10-a8f0-45a4-b490-c5b1d7095e8d</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 22 Aug 2023 20:50:56 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692736598</ingested><modified> 2023-08-22T20:36:42+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f9ff4450-4127-11ee-9f7e-8ecd39d005c8" width="3840"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f9ff4450-4127-11ee-9f7e-8ecd39d005c8" width="3840"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Heart Machine / Gearbox Publishing]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Marketing still from the upcoming game ‘Hyper Light Breaker.’ A humanoid character with a red body and long blue hair gazes at a forboding red sky with purple beams coming down from the clouds.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Hyper Light Breaker]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Amazon, Meta and others face scrutiny for allowing sellers to list recalled products]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>互联网零售商收到了有关其召回产品的方法的质疑。众议院能源和商业委员会已<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://energycommerce.house.gov/posts/e-and-c-bipartisan-leaders-demand-online-marketplaces-divulge-efforts-to-remove-harmful-recalled-products-from-platforms">致函</a>亚马逊、Ebay、Meta、沃尔玛和其他在线购物门户网站，询问他们为阻止在其平台上销售召回和违禁商品所做的努力。他们尤其担心，据称 Meta 未能阻止 Facebook Marketplace 销售两种召回的儿童产品：Fisher-Price Rock &#39;n Play sleeper 和 Boppy Newborn Lounger。</p><p>消费品安全委员会 (CPSC) 于 2019 年召回了 Rock &#39;n Play，并于 2021 年召回了 Newborn Lounger。不过，该委员会表示，下架请求率（平均每月 1,000 个）并未放缓，而且还没有放缓。没有任何阻止销售的“积极措施”。大约 100 起婴儿死亡事件与摇滚乐有关。包括委员会主席凯西·麦克莫里斯·罗杰斯在内的国会议员担心，在线市场可能会因为在阻止这些销售方面采取的措施太少而将儿童和所有用户置于危险之中。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> The House representatives ask all the companies to detail their current efforts to block sales of recalled products, including the presence of dedicated staff. The politicians also want to know what the companies will do in the future and whether there&#39;s any legal uncertainty about how to tackle the problems. The letters ask if the companies are willing to work with the committee on a solution to the problem. The companies have been told to respond no later than August 31st.</p><p> In a statement to Engadget, a Meta spokesperson says that sales of recalled goods aren&#39;t unique to Facebook Marketplace. The representative says Meta takes the issue &quot;seriously&quot; and pulls listings that violate its rules. Ebay tells Engadget it takes recalls &quot;very seriously&quot; and uses a combination of AI and investigators to spot potentially unsafe listings. It hoped to work with the House committee on these issues.</p><p> The enquiries come just as Amazon is facing a <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-will-reportedly-meet-with-the-ftc-ahead-of-potential-antitrust-lawsuit-190316632.html">potential antitrust lawsuit</a> over its sales practices, and amid greater effort to scrutinize tech giants&#39; behavior. Meta has also been scaling back some of its shopping features, including the shutdowns of live shopping <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/facebook-live-shopping-ends-october-2022-202501693.html">on Facebook</a> and <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/instagram-live-shopping-shutdown-205824247.html">Instagram</a> . Those closures are cost-cutting efforts, but they also leave the company&#39;s remaining commerce initiatives in a more fragile position.</p><p> <strong>Update 8/22 5PM ET:</strong> We&#39;ve updated the story with a statement from Ebay.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/amazon-meta-and-others-face-scrutiny-for-allowing-sellers-to-list-recalled-products-202005944.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/amazon-meta-and-others-face-scrutiny-for-allowing-sellers-to-list-recalled-products-202005944.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 85b7eb3c-54ff-4305-a855-714710ca925e</guid><dc:creator> Jon Fingas</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 22 Aug 2023 20:20:05 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692738057</ingested><modified> 2023-08-22T21:01:05+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="3780" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-07/f7522110-e6a1-11eb-bfff-edb16fd0a4d3" width="6720"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![C